  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "Quarry outside Boden. Dries quickly. The crag faces southwest. Chipping at a whole new level! Higher up on the same mountain is Åbergsfortet, which can be a good alternative if the heat is uncomfortable and the wind doesn’t quite reach the quarry.",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:aberget"
        ]
      },
      "sections": {
        "allmant": {
          "title": {
            "text": "General",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:aberget"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Quarried rock outside Boden. Dries quickly. The crag faces southwest. Chipping at a whole new level! Higher up on the same mountain is Åbergsfortet, which can be a good alternative if the heat is tough and the wind doesn't quite reach the quarry.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:aberget"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Access",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:aberget"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "From Luleå, drive past the first intersection in Sävast (by the golf course). At the next intersection, turn left. Follow Sävastvägen through the village. When the houses on the left end, it's about 3.5 km until you should turn right. Just before the turn, there’s a stable and some paddocks on the right. The asphalt access road appears with a gentle right turn. Follow it for 100 m, then take the left onto a sandy/stony road. The crag should be visible through the trees from here. Park and walk, or if you have a decent vehicle, you can drive all the way to the crag (in which case, turn right after 20 m).",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:aberget"
            ]
          }
        },
        "leder": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Routes",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:aberget"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Many route names are painted on the crag, making it easy to navigate. Routes run from left to right. A topo is available in the guide at www.borrbult.nu (Fyrkanten guide - Sport climbing).",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:aberget"
            ]
          }
        },
